metadata.name: long as he had
metadata.description:
memories of his previous life, he believed that one day, he could reach those heights again and even make a real breakthrough!



And at the moment, Su Han is sitting there, eyes slightly closed, like did not hear the arguments of those elders.



Behind him, there was a group of young men and women gloating at him, their mouths from time to time raised a sneering smile.
